    "": "",
    // 教程
    "Antimatter Dimensions are your production units in game. The 1st Antimatter Dimension produces your antimatter.\nEach consecutive Antimatter Dimension produces the previous one, allowing you to have steady growth.\nThere are eight Antimatter Dimensions total.": "反物质维度是您在游戏中的生产单位。 第一个反物质维度产生你的反物质。\n每个连续的反物质维度产生前一个反物质维度，让你有稳定的增长。\n总共有八个反物质维度。",
    "Antimatter is a resource that is throughout the entire game for purchasing various things as you progress. You start\nwith 10 antimatter when you first open the game. And you can\nspend it to buy the 1st Antimatter Dimension to start the game.": "反物质是贯穿整个游戏的一种资源，可在您进行游戏时购买各种物品。 首次打开游戏时，\n您有 10 个反物质。 您可以用它\n购买第一个反物质维度来开始游戏。",
    "Beside the Dimension there is a multiplier (example: 1st Dimension ×1.0).\nThe base production of each Dimension is multiplied by this number.\nThis multiplier increases by ×2 for every 10 of that Dimension purchased.\nEach time this occurs, the price of the dimension will increase.": "在维度旁边有一个乘数（例如：第1维度×1.0）。\n每个维度的基本产量乘以这个数字。\每购买10个维度，该乘数增加×2。\每次发生这种情况，维度的价格都会增加。",
    "Cost & until 10:": "成本 & 买到 10:",
    "Dimension base prices:": "维度基础价格：",
    "Dimension Growth Percent:": "维度增长百分比：",
    "Dimension Multiplier:": "维度乘数：",
    " are gained by resetting your Antimatter Dimensions and Dimension Boosts. They\n      improve the effectiveness of your Tickspeed Upgrades in a compounding way.": "通过重置反物质维度和维度提升获得。它们以复合方式提高 计数频率 升级的效率。",
    "Autobuyers are a built-in feature to the game which purchases upgrades for your Antimatter\n      Dimensions automatically when you can afford them.": "自动购买者是游戏的一个内置功能，当您有能力时，它会自动为您的反物质维度购买升级。",
    "Every Antimatter Dimension continuously produces Dimensions of the next tier down. The lowest\n      Antimatter Dimension produces antimatter.": "每个反物质维度持续产生下一层维度。最低的反物质维度产生反物质。",
    "s are gained by resetting all your Antimatter Dimensions and tickspeed after\n      reaching a certain amount of the highest available Antimatter Dimension. They provide a multiplier to your\n      Antimatter Dimensions.": "在达到最高可用反物质维度的一定数量后，通过重置所有反物质维度和计数频率获得。它们为您的反物质维度提供了乘数。",
    "for buy until 10 Xth Dimension\n(you can also hold down Shift while buying Dimensions, which will only buy\n1 instead of 10),": "对于购买到第10个维度\n（您也可以在购买维度时按住Shift键，这样只会购买\n1而不是10），",
    "for Max all": "对于 全部最大",
    "Max all will buy until 10 of the 1st Antimatter Dimension until it can't anymore,\nthen second, and so on until the 8th Antimatter Dimension, and then buy max Tickspeed Upgrades.": "全部最大 将一直购买到第1个反物质维度的10个，直到它无法再购买，\n第二个，以此类推，直到第8个反物质维，然后购买最大 计数频率 升级。",
    "Max all:": "全部最大：",
    "Next to each accumulated quantity of owned Dimensions,\nthe amount of that Dimension purchased toward the next multiplier upgrade is displayed in brackets.\nFor example if you have (4) next to your accumulated dimension quantity,\nyou'll need 6 more of that dimension for the next multiplier increase.": "在所拥有维度的每个累积数量旁边，\n该维度在下一次乘数升级中购买的金额显示在括号中。\例如，如果您的累积维度数量旁边有（4），\n您将需要该维度的6倍才能进行下一次乘数增加。",
    "Purchased Dimensions Quantity:": "购买的维度数量：",
    "The next column is your current amount of that Dimension you own.\nThis is a combination of how many you have purchased with antimatter,\nas well as produced from the higher Dimension.": "下一列是你当前拥有的那个维度的数量。\n这是你用反物质购买的数量的组合，\n以及从更高的维度产生的数量。",
    "This number represents the amount of growth that each\nDimension experiences per second. 100% means the dimension is doubling each second.\nThis allows you to judge overall growth.": "此数字表示每个\n维度每秒经历的增长量。 100% 表示维度每秒翻一番。\n这使您可以判断总体增长。",
    "You can buy a single quantity of each Dimension with antimatter when the cost button is highlighted.\nAlternatively, if the Until 10 button is highlighted,\nyou can buy whatever quantity gets you to that Dimension's next Dimension multiplier.": "当成本按钮突出显示时，您可以购买单个数量的每个维度的反物质。\n或者，如果“直到 10”按钮突出显示，\n您可以购买任何数量让您达到该维度的下一个维度乘数。",
